summary: Daedric Arrows are Enhanced with new Spells hope you like it.
descriptionHtml:
Daedric Arrows are Enhanced with new Spells
4 types of arrow are available those are
FireballArrow,FireStormArrow,IceSpikeArrow and LightArrow
You can find it in a ArrowBarrel at infront of The Drunken Huntsman or you can Buy it in The Drunken Huntsman..
A test Video for Enhanced Arrows    http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=X172LHZ_uHU
Good Luck.........
